            <div class="collapsible-content">
                <p><strong>Product Overview:</strong> FSTL’s Back-Up Title Guarantee protects buyers, lenders, and investors in cases where the primary title is incomplete, pending registration, or partially defective.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Coverage:</strong> Defective, unregistered, or disputed titles.</li>
                    <li><strong>Eligibility:</strong> Titles under verification or with minor documentation gaps.</li>
                    <li><strong>Benefits:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Legal and financial indemnity in case of title issues.</li>
                            <li>Facilitates investment and financing on pending titles.</li>
                            <li>Enhances lender and investor confidence in uncertain title conditions.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Activation:</strong> Purchase via secure FSTL Payment Methods.</li>
                </ul>
                <p><em>The Back-Up Title Guarantee ensures continuity, trust, and flexibility in property transactions, complementing the Primary Title Guarantee.</em></p>
            </div>
        </section>

